&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role / Position overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;53&quot; data-end=&quot;236&quot;&gt;FT Specialist is offering an internal opportunity to join its Journalism Fellowship Program, a one-year rotational program running from &lt;strong data-start=&quot;189&quot; data-end=&quot;235&quot;&gt;September 7, 2026, through August 27, 2027&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
