&lt;li&gt;No prior journalism experience required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong desire to learn and grow within the field of journalism.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eagerness to uncover and communicate compelling stories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity about business and economic topics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
