&lt;li&gt;Experience creating bespoke data visualisations and multimedia layouts using React or similar web frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Numeracy and data-handling skills, including experience with programming languages such as R or Python, and the ability to think statistically.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
