&lt;li&gt;Working with the latest AI tools while maintaining responsibility for quality and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desirable but not essential&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
